{"title":"JavaScript Event Delegation (事件委派)","uid":"09ad92d6e7d17dc3779c181e08a79bd5","slug":"JavaScript-Event-Delegation-事件委派","date":"2021-04-11T12:08:07.000Z","updated":"2022-06-13T13:59:22.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/JavaScript-Event-Delegation-事件委派.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p>Event Delegation（事件委派）是一種受惠於 Event Bubbling 而能減少監聽器數目的方法。</p>\n<iframe height=\"265\" style=\"width: 100%;\" scrolling=\"no\" title=\"Event Delegation\" src=\"https://codepen.io/michael-luo/embed/mdRXyXR?height=265&theme-id=dark&default-tab=css,result\" frameborder=\"no\" loading=\"lazy\" allowtransparency=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\">\n  See the Pen <a href='https://codepen.io/michael-luo/pen/mdRXyXR'>Event Delegation</a> by Michael Luo\n  (<a href='https://codepen.io/michael-luo'>@michael-luo</a>) on <a href='https://codepen.io'>CodePen</a>.\n</iframe>\n\n\n<p>當我們 click 不同的小區塊時，就會 console 出它們個別的名字，例如：a、b 或 c。</p>\n<p>實作方法是將:</p>\n<p>click 事件綁在 parent 上，藉由 Event Bubbling 傳遞給 child，而非直接將事件綁定在 child 上。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>優點是可減少監聽器的數目，</li>\n<li>缺點是由於需要判斷哪些 child node 是我們有興趣的項目，而必須多寫一些程式碼做判斷。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>在此範例中，我們加上一個 <code>filter.child</code>，表示只對有<code>.child</code>這個 class 的節點有興趣，<br>而沒有加上<code>.child</code>的節點則不被影響，例如<code>click.subitem</code>這個節點之後就不會 console 它的名字。</p>\n","text":"Event Delegation（事件委派）是一種受惠於 Event Bubbling 而能減少監聽器數目的方法。 See the Pen Event Delegation by Michael Luo (@michael-luo) on CodePen. 當我們 click 不...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":439,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"JavaScript","slug":"JavaScript","count":45,"path":"api/categories/JavaScript.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"JavaScript","slug":"JavaScript","count":41,"path":"api/tags/JavaScript.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"Michael","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"happy coding!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Michael0520","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wecha